<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">«وَاللَّائِي يَئِسْنَ»</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> واحدها ذات..<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">«وَأُولاتُ الْأَحْمالِ»</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> واحدها ذات..<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">«مِنْ وُجْدِكُمْ»</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> من سعتكم، من الجدة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>